      <title>Michael Saylor 称，任何时候购买比特币都是正确的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/there-s-never-a-bad-time-to-buy-bitcoin-michael-saylor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy 执行主席兼联合创始人 Michael Saylor 表示，就长期资本管理而言，比特币是最佳选择。他在彭博电视台发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/there-s-never-a-bad-time-to-buy-bitcoin-michael-saylor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:06:27 GMT</pubDate>
