      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/panel-to-help-who-consider-if-african-mpox-outbreak-is-emergency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界卫生组织将召集一个顾问小组，帮助确定中非地区爆发的致命牛痘疫情是否构成国际紧急情况。]]></description>
